dcterms:creator: R. G. Krishnan
U. Shalit
D. Sontag
dcterms:description: A dataset containing sequences of polyphonic music represented as 88-dimensional binary vectors corresponding to piano notes, used for training deep Markov models.
dcterms:title: Polyphonic Music Dataset

dcterms:creator: E. N. Lorenz
dcterms:description: A dataset representing the 3-space Lorenz attractor, a chaotic system modeled by three ordinary differential equations, used for parameter and state estimation in deep learning frameworks.
dcterms:title: 3-space Lorenz attractor
